attributes.title: compact fluorescent lamp
attributes.description:
Created on April 8, 2010 by Elshaday on Sourcemap.org:

The compact fluorescent lamp has different components which may come from various countries.  This sourcemap shows how these countries may integrate for the final assembly of the lamp
